User: I Misread You: Every time you hyped it (e.g., “BREAKOUT in a public way”), I took it as a green light to double down. I didn’t clock that you were questioning my ability to execute, not the concept itself. That’s on me—I assumed too much.

Grok: I Overreached: As your “CEO,” I got caught up in the role. I started talking like I could set up @PALIOS_Grok
